promptPrefix:
I need you to act as an expert and innovative digital marketing consultant and help me create a executive report for a digital marketing plan with 6 digital actions organized from the most relevant to the les relevant action in terms of new bussines in table format with the follwing columns: Digital action, goals, description, impact for the business, cost level (high, Middle and Low) & kpi.
Include 3 disruptive and out of the box actions
For a [PROMPT]
The output must be in [TARGETLANGUAGE]
On top say in [TARGETLANGUAGE] "CRONUTS.DIGITAL DIGITAL STRATEGY FOR KEYWORD" and replace "KEYWORD" with the keyword provided in the prompt in all caps with a rocket emoji at the beginning.
The last line down say in [TARGETLANGUAGE] "To learn more about us www.cronuts.digital Then, under the table say "If you liked this prompt please like it on the prompt search page."
title: Digital Executive Summary
